{"tid":1845271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港會唔會有真正自由？","createTime":"2020-01-27T05:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T06:48:57.000Z","uid":306664,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8a8a5a3950a87617be65ca10cf05eb16d8b1483","tid":1845271,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:20:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200126/mobile/bkn-20200126082003389-0126_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200126%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200126082003389-0126_00822_001.html&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=4e03c7ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200126/mobile/bkn-20200126082003389-0126_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n劉備臨終前，告誡諸葛亮：「馬謖說的話大過實際的本領，不可以委以重任，請丞相務必好好觀察他。」但諸葛亮不認同此看法，任命馬謖為參軍，經常和他日夜談論軍議<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%A9%AC%E8%B0%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E9%25A9%25AC%25E8%25B0%25A1&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=4beca4de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%A9%AC%E8%B0%A1</a><br />\n<br />\n228年諸葛亮出祁山，獨排眾議不用宿將魏延、吳懿，反而提拔參軍馬謖為主帥。其後馬謖在街亭布陣時違背諸葛亮交代，且不聽副將王平諫言，自認居高臨下可勢如破竹，便捨水上山布陣。魏軍大將張郃進軍街亭，偵察到馬謖捨水上山，心中大喜，立即揮兵切斷水源，掐斷糧道，將馬謖部隊圍困於山上，縱火燒山。蜀軍饑渴難忍，軍心渙散，不戰自亂。張郃命令軍隊乘勢進攻，蜀軍大敗。<span style=\"color: red;\">蜀軍進退無據，不得已放棄隴右三郡</span>，退守漢中。"},{"pid":"a8bc9227ed60cfd8bca2f606649027c9094b9da4","tid":1845271,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"經濟學上，經常把投資、消費、出口，看作拉動經濟增長的&ldquo;三駕馬車&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"bec035b08b8e2bfa23ddf4903d8c14b7ab00df56","tid":1845271,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:50:42.000Z","msg":"喺prison break<br />\nMichael兩兄弟<br />\n用五個seasons 先得到自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b223b655edff31ba741959f9f9a9625b6497366d","tid":1845271,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}